docs {
  # List Submissions

  Returns all benchmark submissions linking systems to models with results.

  ## Data Shape

  ```json
  [
    {
      "id": "sub-001",
      "systemId": "system1",
      "modelId": "deepseek-r1",
      "submissionDate": "2026-01-15T10:30:00Z",
      "publishDate": "2026-03-16T00:00:00Z",
      "resultValid": true
    }
  ]
  ```

  ## Fields

  | Field | Type | Description |
  |-------|------|-------------|
  | id | string | Unique submission identifier |
  | systemId | string | Reference to system |
  | modelId | string | Reference to ML model |
  | submissionDate | string | ISO 8601 timestamp of submission |
  | publishDate | string | ISO 8601 timestamp of publication |
  | resultValid | boolean | Whether results passed validation |

  ## Relationships

  - Links to `systems` via `systemId`
  - Links to `models` via `modelId`
  - Referenced by `paretoCurves` via `submissionId`

  ## Filter Examples

  - `?systemId=system1` - Submissions for a specific system
  - `?modelId=deepseek-r1` - Submissions for a specific model
  - `?resultValid=true` - Only valid submissions
}
